name: DataLakePreview
description: Preview a datalake export. Use this service sparingly. Not all models can be previewed. This is only for testing purposes. Only a single ID can be specified at a time
auth_description: Requires a user of type `Employee` or `Api` with functionality `DataLakePreview:None`

headers.name: EVA-User-Agent
headers.description: The user agent that is making these calls. Don't make this specific per device/browser but per application. This should be of the form: `MyFirstUserAgent/1.0.0`

headers.name: EVA-Requested-OrganizationUnitID
headers.description: The ID of the organization unit to run this request in.

headers.name: EVA-Requested-OrganizationUnit-Query
headers.description: The query that selects the organization unit to run this request in.

headers.name: EVA-IDs-Mode
headers.description: The IDs mode to run this request in. Currently only `ExternalIDs` is supported.

headers.name: EVA-IDs-BackendSystemID
headers.description: The ID of the backend system that is used to resolve the IDs.

B.name: FinancialPeriodID
B.description: This is the ID of a `FinancialPeriod`

B.name: OrderID
B.description: This is the ID of a `Order`

B.name: StockMutationID
B.description: This is the ID of a `StockMutation`

B.name: UserID
B.description: This is the ID of a `User`

D.name: Code
D.description: A unique ID identifying this error.

D.name: Message
D.description: A human-readable message describing the error.

D.name: RequestID
D.description: A unique ID identifying the request. Please provide this ID when contacting support.

D.name: Type
D.description: A short description of the error type.

R.name: ExternalIDs
R.description: When using the `ExternalIDs` mode, this will hold the resolved external IDs.

R.name: IsAsyncResultAvailable
R.description: This is a flag indicating whether the async request is done. If it is `null`, it is not an async service. If it is `false`, the response is not yet available. Do not process the properties in that case. It is is `true` the properties are filled with the result of the call.

R.name: UnresolvedExternalIDs
R.description: When using the `ExternalIDs` mode, this will hold the external IDs we couldn't resolve.

Z.name: Amount
Z.description: Amount of tax for this rate

BF.name: IsOrdered
BF.description: Don't use this, rely on `IsCarryOut` and `IsDelivery` instead

BF.name: IsReservation
BF.description: Don't use this, rely on `IsCarryOut` and `IsDelivery` instead
